{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-disagreement/task-77","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-express-disagreement","challengeType":19,"description":"","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">True, but...</span> To je način da pokažete saglasnost dok dodajete drugačiju perspektivu. Ovaj izraz pomaže da se diskusije održavaju jasnim i balansiranima. Na primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>James:</strong> <span class=\"highlighted-text\">AI can automate a lot of tasks in software development.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Eve:</strong> <span class=\"highlighted-text\">True, but human oversight is still necessary to catch errors AI might miss.</span> — Ova osoba priznaje da AI pomaže, ali podseća da je ljudski nadzor i dalje neophodan.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>","helpCategory":"English","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte audio odgovor na pitanje ispod.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-disagreement/task-77"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Anna se ne slaže sa Davidom dok zadržava svoju perspektivu. Šta bi trebalo da kaže?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">True, but the office isn't the only place to build team spirit.</span></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":"EN2aa5f9dd"},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">You're right, so there's no need for remote work at all.</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Anna i dalje daje prednost radu na daljinu i želi da pokaže da se timski duh može graditi i na druge načine, a ne samo u kancelariji.</p>","audioId":"EN8886eb97"}],"solution":1}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"interview-room3.png","characters":[{"character":"David","position":{"x":50,"y":0,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"B1_11-2.